Class Rectangle

java.lang.Object

public class Rectangle
extends java.lang.Object

Class that represents a rectangular or square area of display or anything else of interest with a rectangular shape.

Method Detail

contains

public boolean contains(int x,
                        int y,
                        int gap)
Checks whether the given coordinate falls within this Rectangles area leaving a margin of gap pixels on all sides of this Rectangle

Parameters:
x - the x coordinate of the point
y - the y coordinate of the point
gap - the gap/ margin in pixels to be left on all sides of the rectangle before the check
Returns:
true if the coordinate is contained within this Rectangle and false otherwise

equals
